Nessus - Proprietary vulnerability scanner
Installation: https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Nessus
Pricing: https://www.tenable.com/products/nessus

Installation:
  yay -S nessus
  sudo systemctl enable --now nessusd.service
  https://localhost:8834   Visit this site
  https://www.tenable.com/products/nessus/activation-code
                           Register your email and wait for your key to be emailed to you
  sudo systemctl stop nessusd.service 
                           Stop the service before doing anything with nessuscli
  nessuscli fetch --register ACTIVATION_CODE
                           Activate the license
  nessuscli fetch --code-in-use
                           View your current license activation code
  nessuscli update --plugins-only
                           Update the plugins
  sudo systemctl start nessusd.service 
                           Start the service Log in back to the website
